---
title: Roasted Chili Brussel Sprouts and Sprouted Brown Rice in a Herb Vinaigrette
description: Who said that brussel sprouts were boring?! We don't think so! Roasting this winter green with a pinch of salt and chili flakes turns this sometimes maligned veg into the hero of the dish! Coupled with the goodness of a sprouted brown rice in a herb vinaigrette, you will literally have a thought-changing experience!
